{"tid":2066407,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"「磨牙」符合國情 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-06-16T09:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T09:11:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c96e9e8fa0c0ec44ca9130a339bec293c7fc8a51","tid":2066407,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200616/20937926/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200616%2F20937926%2F&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aawEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=a44ae6c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200616%2F20937926%2F&h=be03627e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200616/20937926/</a><br />\n<br />\n「磨牙」符合國情 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200616/large/1592204927_b222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200616%2Flarge%2F1592204927_b222.jpg&h=a8a339d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看到一段娛圈新聞──但原來這不是八卦新聞。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸28歲女星鄭爽，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，都顯不出《微微一笑很傾城》的原貌了。<br />\n<br />\n這裏不是說整容，而是「磨牙」──她養了柴犬枸杞，帶牠到寵物店洗牙時，竟然希望枸杞的牙別太鋒利，「怕牠咬到我」，問職員是否可幫牠磨牙？因為有些動物短片中，其他人可以將手伸進犬隻口中，其他小狗那麼乖枸杞就那麼兇，所以磨平牙齒安全些。結果這綜藝節目播出後一致負評，被罵慘了。<br />\n<br />\n儍白甜女星賣萌裝可愛是常態，但這回太無知又不負責任了。沒養寵物也知動物有天性也有特點，犬齒當然尖利，但既養狗，怕牠咬人，應耐心引導和訓練，而非對付其生理結構，罔顧其感受及啃骨頭所需，不人道。<br />\n<br />\n但想深一層，小狗屬於自己的，愛怎麼整治怎麼調教，關上門是「家事」，豈容旁人說三道四？正如主子受不了民眾發聲，把你們磨牙割舌又如何？非常符合國情。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}